PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of JENNIFER CORSON, of Haliax, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Elizabeth Ann Carmichael, whose term has expired.
